<concept id="system_requirements">
	<title><keyword keyref="product_name_long"/>Supported Configurations </title>
	<shortdesc id="shortdesc_92D228BA03E642648E4843A72B96D5F6"><keyword keyref="product_name_long"/>
		is supported on a variety of platforms. </shortdesc>
	<conbody>
		<p>The supported configurations tables are organized by the 32-bit and 64-bit platforms on
			which <keyword keyref="product_name_long"/> standalone runs. </p>
		<ul id="ul_BEAF012B69214636BCAD2D14A9ABBC08">
			<li><xref href="#system_requirements/section_937FF0E606164F3EA0A965AA7DDD246D"
					format="dita"/></li>
			<li><xref href="#system_requirements/section_j1b_4p3_tq" type="section" format="dita"
				/></li>
			<li><xref href="#system_requirements/section_cg1_zp3_tq" type="section" format="dita"
				/></li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			<note>Running <keyword keyref="product_name_long"/> clusters with a mix of different
				platforms is not recommended. Use a consistent platform on all machines in your
				cluster. </note>
		</p>
