		<section id="section_j1b_4p3_tq">
			<title>Java Support Notes</title>
			<p><keyword keyref="product_name_long"/>
				<keyword keyref="product_version"/> requires Java SE 7.</p>
			<p>The <keyword keyref="product_name_long"/> does not include Java. You must download
				and install a supported JRE or JDK on each system running <keyword
					keyref="product_name_long"/>. <keyword keyref="product_name_long"/> recommends
				the installation of a full JDK (and not just a JRE) to obtain better performance
				with <codeph>gfsh</codeph>
				<codeph>status</codeph> and <codeph>stop</codeph> commands.</p>
		</section>
		<section id="section_cg1_zp3_tq">
			<title>Filesystem Type for Linux and Solaris Platforms</title>
			<p>For optimal disk-store performance, we recommend the use of <codeph>ext4</codeph>
				filesystems when operating on Linux or Solaris platforms.</p>
